Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:30.04,lt,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.15\blur0.8\fscx50\fscy50\b1\frz20.2\c&H515356&\pos(865,559)}Shakespeare's {\fax0.18}comedies {\fax0.22}are {\fax0.25}boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.04,lt,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.08\blur0.8\fscx50\fscy50\b1\frz18.06\c&H6E6E6E&\pos(613,254)\clip(346,156,397,361)\t(30,2900,\clip(346,156,812,361))}Not only {\fax0.1}are {\fax0.11}they {\fax0.14}interesting, {\fax0.16}but {\fax0.18}they're {\fax0.22}especially {\alpha&HFF&\fax0.25}cruel.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.96,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only are they interesting, but they're especially cruel.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.41,md,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.11\fad(500,0)\blur1.5\b1\c&H4B4D52&\fscx300\fscy300\frz18.07\pos(984,577)}cruel
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.41,md,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.11\fad(500,0)\blur1.5\b1\c&HCCD995&\fscx300\fscy300\frz18.07\pos(981,578)}cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.41,md,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.11\fad(500,0)\blur1.5\b1\c&H8A7ECB&\fscx300\fscy300\frz18.07\pos(987,576)}cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But why aren't you looking it up in the database?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an Inspector. You have authorization, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I access those files, Kougami will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want him to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you that concerned about Ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you even been in love, Kagari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Akane. I'm more experienced in life than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only love. I've done all sorts of bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've glimpsed into a world that a wholesome girl like you can't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's alcohol. Real alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ol' Masaoka shared it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, people are afraid of getting addicted to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so they stick to safe therapeutic tripping or go virtual, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for drinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for blowing fire?{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now's when we get to enjoy vices like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}real{\i0} cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! I told you, those snacks are for drinkers only!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoilsport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or would you like to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get drunk, I might start talking about all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When I started here, Ko had already been stripped of his position as Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I heard that an Enforcer who was under him at the time got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. He was going after a culprit, but ended up as a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, his name was Sasayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.03,0:06:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed in the same manner as the other victims. I heard it was terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So it messed Ko up and his Crime Coefficient went way too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:07:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That case was never solved, but Ko's still investigating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you drink so much and still be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You just get drunk too easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Enforcer Sasayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's no way I could forget the Specimen Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Specimen Case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we, and the detectives, referred to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what plastination is, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a process used to create biological specimens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It's a technique for preserving tissue by impregnating it with resin.{i'd impregnate her with my resin, if you know what i mean}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the Specimen Case, this process was used to commit grotesque murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They first dismembered and cut open the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they used plastination\N to turn it into a human specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they brought it right into the middle of town and displayed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath a Holographic illumination used in the entertainment district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands of passersby{passed by} thought they were just looking at environment Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But in truth, there was a dismembered body right underneath it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When that got out, the area stress jumped up four levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so bad that they even imposed a news ban.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I asked about it while you were eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yayoi wouldn't get worked up over something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She's into more violent and passionate stuff.{wut}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were talking about the Specimen Case, right? Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since it was obviously done by an expert,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the investigation focused on experts in pharmacology and chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, Sasayama was killed while working on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, while investigating a totally unrelated report regarding a missing high school teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,they came across plastination resin in his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this guy. Touma Kouzaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after he went missing, the crimes stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no doubt he was the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But all we had was circumstantial evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, it remains an unsolved case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, Touma didn't know anything about chemistry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so even the question of who created the resin remains a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that there was an accomplice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if we can really call them an "accomplice"{until dou ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when we don't even know if they understood what their resin would be used for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It remains a mystery as to how it was acquired too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, God only knows.{love is a such a sweet illusion}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're having a rough time as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering how gloomy you look, it'd be hard not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Being on the fast track is tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to keep lots of things confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this still about that erratic colleague of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know what to make of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, it seems like he was once in the same position as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this troublemaker used to be an honor student
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,whose test scores were over 700 or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! That kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a thought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you and your subordinate are quite similar?{she just fucking said that. goddamn you, script}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's urgent! I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it up to you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Kuzuhara Satsuki is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard the teachers have been ordered to keep silent about it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so as not to worry the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That worries us even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The selling point of this school{until gakkou tte sa}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is that they keep girls of susceptible age isolated from society in a conservatory environment{until kakuri shite}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to prevent their Psycho-Passes from getting cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So they sweep problems under the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They also need to keep up appearances in front of our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some other rumors that are pretty scary too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the teachers who used to teach in this school was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ouryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miss Rikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why Ouryou Rikako is so popular.{her name is "oryo" so she must be evil. calling it now}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty, she's smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little afraid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes her eyes just look so empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they're staring into a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawarazaki. Shimotsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of you belong to any clubs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Educational organizations that have club activities like our school, Ousou Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are very rare these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be a shame to miss out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you recruiting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the president of the art club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like, please come and see us in our club room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Shimotsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I sometimes get absorbed in thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not like I'm looking into a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an alien, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy, Mika! She heard you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's new husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you took... notice of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, since I've been watching you all this time, Yoshika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ouryou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That man... he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly looks at me... with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,o... obscene eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I go home, there's signs that someone was in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it anymore... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't talk to your mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The debt my biological father left us is so big
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that my mother couldn't hope to repay it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to depend on that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But at last week's regular check up, my Psycho-Pass was very cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshika.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you can't choose the life you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how hard that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In this era, the System determines everyone's aptitudes {until dare mo ka}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and we all have no choice but to live by it{until sotte}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and be satisfied with whatever "happiness" is forced upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as we are unable to make our real dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to discover the person you desire to be?{until jibun no kachi}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to realize your true worth?{until omowanai}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the true beauty that's hiding inside you, Yoshika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I tell you more about Shakespeare's works?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Titus Andronicus"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The character I like in it is Titus's daughter, Lavinia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She got dragged into trouble because of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy raped her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,cut out her tongue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and cut off her arms as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was my deer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Lavinia.{kawaisou ni}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She was killed by her own father.{lavinia wa jibun no chichi ni korosareru no}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tons of things that humans can do but animals can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them is safety control.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it is, humans have always put a safety device on it.{rule 253}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Enforcers are also equipped with a safety device called Inspectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the point, the drones you controlled were equipped with rigorous safety controls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those drones were supposed to be completely safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet, this memory card made them kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you obtain it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have the safety canceller that Kanehara used in the Hachiouji Drone incident
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mido's Holograph cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In both cases, I could only recover a bit of the source code,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are clear similarities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:17:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the same programmer wrote the code for both.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd bet the bra I'm wearing today on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that Mido was obsessed with social networks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but he wasn't skilled enough to mess with public Holo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt that both Kanehara and Mido were being backed by a professional cyber-criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But this testimony of Kanehara's isn't going to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling the truth! I just got it one day in the mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter had no name or return address.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It just said that it was from someone with a grudge against that factory
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who wanted to mess up that place together with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty vicious for someone who'd commit crimes just for kicks, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How could the sender predict that Kanehara would kill in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops figured out Kanehara just by checking the records of the staff's periodic checkups.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There was someone else who could do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That periodic checkup record wasn't confidential, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what was this guy's motive for helping Mido?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Kanehara and Mido who had the motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've been enough reason for {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The intent and means to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To create a crime by bringing those two otherwise separate things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's {\i1}his{\i0} goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gino, this is the same as that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone who seeks out those who have not yet found a way to manifest their desire to kill,{until ataeru}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and grants them the means to become real killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down and think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, it was a special resin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it was a tool for cracking software.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They're totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.65,lts,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.62\blur1\c&HAAA9A8&\fscx70\fscy70\b1\frz136.2\pos(686.857,300.571)\alpha&H50&}Public Safety Bureau \NSpecial Case 102\h\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The engineer and the middleman are two different people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone who brings together those who want to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who can create the tools they need to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the real mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're chasing a ghost that we don't even know exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasayama was on the brink of figuring it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll settle this for his sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've spent the past three years working toward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Takahashi from the Public Cleaning Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the Central Fountain Tower right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Noise has been appearing in the Hologram for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please turn off the fountain Holo so that we can check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it some sort of artwork? A sculpture?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... but isn't this in kinda bad taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look closely, it looks pretty real, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I wouldn't want to display it at my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Lavinia was happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,having been freed from her violated body?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Because the girl should not survive her shame,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and by her presence still renew her sorrows," was it, Mr. Makishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even beautiful flowers must eventually wither and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the fate of all living beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only natural that one would wish to freeze them in time while they're still blossoming in full glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you really loved her as if she was your own daughter, would you too say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kill'd her, for whom my tears have made me blind," as Titus did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that'd be a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because I still have many more drawings to complete in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:46.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,2200)\blur1}It seems all fairy tales {\alpha&HFF&}are dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.67,0:21:50.39,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,900)\blur1\alpha&HFF&}It seems {\alpha&H00&}all fairy tales are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:55.74,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}In a hospital ward of brick stones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:00.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}my voice is too coarse to sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:05.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Outside in the foggy haze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:11.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}a red moon glows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:16.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Look at me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:22.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}Do not avert your gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:26.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Behind black bars
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.59,0:22:29.47,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:31.91,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}I wish there were a punishment for evil
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.71,0:22:34.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Always I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Now, grant us justice
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}before chaos takes us all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:44.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur1}Pay the price of fate and let us go together,
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.92,0:22:49.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,500)\blur1}nameless beasts
